node.text: 👏👏👏thank you for sharing...I'm in the process of exposing a sexual predator/pedaphile...the list goes on. The truth needs to be out there in hopes of preventing him from continuing to do this. You are brave and strong...you did the right thing.💕

Stand up to bullies and abusers👊🏻 I’ve waited four years for this time to come. #metoo #sexualabuse #stopvictimblaming #justicewillbeserved #karma #psychopath #sociopath #survivor #abusesurvivor #speakyourtruth #shareyourstory
Good for you!!!
Awesome !!!
Awesome!!
@the.ketoqueen thank you 💛💛💛
You’re an inspiration ✨🙏🏼✊🏼
@exposing_real_narcs2019 😭😭 this comment made me tear up (good tears)...thank you! your kind words and encouragement mean a lot to me🙏🏻💛
@sociopath.free You are an inspiration!! Wishing you all the best! 💕🌹

You did the absolute right thing! Thank you for your story and strength! You are a survivor and can give other victims the courage to speak out against their abuser! Phenomenal woman... That's you! 🙌🏾🌹

Thank you for your courage. I am increasingly disturbed by the role women play in supporting harmful male authority figures. We can see how the patriarchy really is a whole system not just ‘men’. One awful man and a bunch of women dedicated to ‘money laundering’ his crimes by standing by him and shaming victims and you have the ingredients to exert abuse throughout a whole community. They can’t do it totally on their own.

@youstillhaveworth That’s very kind of you to say and I’m so glad people are reading this story. Yes, you may share the story part but please leave out my picture because the jury trial is still to come and I probably should have left the pic out myself! I should have spent more time editing the story and my poor grammar and English lol but the message is the important part. Thanks in advance for sharing my story and thanks for all you’re doing to raise awareness 🙏🏻💛🙂
Wow! What an amazing story! Would you mind if I shared your story on my blog? I have a section of survivor stories, and I know your story would be a wonderful addition!
You are beyond brave. I have stories too. I relate. I haven't been brave enough. I admire you!! ❤️🙏❤️
I'm a rape survivor so I deeply understand. So sorry you had to go thru any of it. 💜💜💜
